collectionMetadata.name: IPOS applications API
collectionMetadata.description:
This dataset contains APIs for the retrieval for the following type of applications:
- Patents
- Designs
- Trademarks

datasetMetadata.name: Patent applications
datasetMetadata.description: This API allows you to retrieve patent applications by lodgement date.

datasetMetadata.name: Design applications
datasetMetadata.description: This API allows you to retrieve design applications by lodgement date.

datasetMetadata.name: Trademark applications
datasetMetadata.description: This API allows you to retrieve trademark applications by lodgement date.
